text: Mimics Super 1000 is a 1996 Indian Malayalam film directed by Balu Kiriyath and starring Jagadish, Janardhanan and Anusha in the lead roles.http://spicyonion.com/title/mimics-super-1000-malayalam-movie/ ==Cast== * Jagadish as Balakrishnan * Janardhanan as Easwara Kurup * Anusha as Gopika Varma * Zainuddin as Ebrahim * Kalabhavan Narayanankutty as Mimicry artist * Reena (actress) as Arundathi Varma * Idavela Babu as Babu * Baburaj (actor) as Aniyan Kurup * Shammi Thilakan as Val Gopi/CI Gopinathan *VK Sreeraman as Achutha Kurup * Mahesh (actor) as Aniyan Kurup *Biju Narayanan as Himself *Kalabhavan Nawas as Mimicry artist *Kalabhavan Santhosh as Santhosh *Kalabhavan Prajod as Mimicry artist * Shaju as Mimicry artist * Biju Chalakkudy as Mimicry artist * Darshana as Sunitha *Salu Kuttanad as Sukumara Kurup *Priyanka Anoop as Susheela *Kalabhavan Martin as Servant *Nandu Pothuval as Mimicry artist *Manuraj as Mimicry artist ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 films Category:Indian films Category:1990s Malayalam-language films
